EN: He has been following his own principles since he was young.

ZH: 我们必须遵循正确的方法来解决问题。
EN: We must follow the correct approach to solve the problem.

ZH: 这个项目需要遵循一定的工作流程。
EN: This project requires following a certain workflow.

